    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior is clean with only minor surface scratches and a few small rock chips consistent with regular use, while the interior remains in great shape with no tears in the upholstery. Mechanically, the car runs smoothly, shifts well, and all major electronics are fully functional. It\u2019s a reliable choice for anyone looking for a solid, honest vehicle that is ready for the road.",
