    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Get ready for a rewarding weekend project with this vehicle! While currently in poor condition, it serves as an excellent canvas for a full restoration or a valuable treasure trove of parts for your next build. It's priced perfectly for someone with a vision and the skills to bring it back to life or utilize its components. Grab this opportunity to own a piece with great potential at a budget-friendly price!",
